author: Just Jared
title: Who Won the Super Bowl 2017 - Patriots or Falcons?
text:
In one of the most exciting games in recent Super Bowl history, the winner of the game is the New England Patriots!
The Atlanta Falcons were off to an early lead in the game, but the Patriots were able to catch up and tied the game, 28-28, with just a minute left in the fourth quarter.
Just minutes into overtime, the first time overtime has happened in the history of the Super Bowl, the Patriots scored a touchdown and sealed the win!
The final score of the game was 34-28.
WHAT DID YOU THINK of the Super Bowl this year?
